<%= render 'member_mailer/greeting' %>

<p>We need information to complete your Medicaid Community Engagement compliance review.</p>

<p>Please log in to your account at [Portal Link] by [Deadline Date] and do one of the following:</p>
<ol>
  <li>
    <strong style="display: block; margin-bottom: 0.5em;">Report your activities (have evidence ready)</strong>
    You'll enter your hours or income and <strong>upload a document, photo, or PDF</strong>.
    Helpful examples:
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Work/income:</strong> recent pay stub, earnings statement</li>
      <li><strong>Job search/training/education:</strong> enrollment or attendance letter, class schedule</li>
      <li><strong>Volunteering/community service:</strong> letter or email from the organization showing dates and hours</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong style="display: block; margin-bottom: 0.5em;">Check if you're exempt</strong>
    You can walk through some prompts to see if the requirement applies to you (e.g., pregnancy, caring for a young child, medical reasons). If you may be exempt, you'll need to provide supporting documentation.
  </li>
</ol>

<%= render 'member_mailer/signature' %>
